017-09-29T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/470/852/4ce.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F000%2F470%2F852%2F4ce.gif&h=d9871db0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be01b91a8d12e09564b01d1e48effa51a6354120","tid":417952,"uid":77630,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"泛民總辭啦"},{"pid":"ef3fac3be904fa558fb2728f68ff739594588657","tid":417952,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰被控「侮辱國旗罪」及「侮辱區旗罪」，案件在東區裁判法院裁決，鄭松泰被裁定兩項罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鄭念慈表示，同意控方所指，玷污的意思等同玷辱，即是與旗幟有實體接觸，但不止限於實質上的玷辱。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又指，被告以玷污方式侮辱國旗及區旗，相信被告自己亦明白這點，即使他當時行為如何小心翼翼，或者有意吸引其他議員返回議事廳，他的行為已構成公開侮辱國旗和區旗。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，去年10月19日，鄭松泰在立法會會議廳內，公開及故意以玷污的方式侮辱國旗及區旗。"},{"pid":"e5b4b50e461d8d92288e9eeb3ad8efaf6b101ea3","tid":417952,"uid":39576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"蝗上有無野講?"},{"pid":"474b649bd0a5b266bb0e692565dc24057e2922e4","tid":417952,"uid":26451,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b51c92265c7c71b6a5122259469bdfc67de0d27","tid":417952,"uid":51532,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aeb3033c6828a6e43991f5933f42ec8b6698b2","tid":417952,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝗上有無野講?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好cut資助呀 如果唔係反面"},{"pid":"7b262a9f8859bb11cbe78737eb51577bf939190a","tid":417952,"uid":27731,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"最好全港議員都係建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持特區政府嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agre